Title: Mens Casio G-Shock green dial world time watch GD-400MB-1ER
Description: chapelle_jewellery Visit our eBay Shop Add us to your Favourites list > Subscribe to our Newsletter > About Chapelle Delivery The Chapelle Guarantee Mens Casio G-Shock green dial world time watch GD-400MB-1ER RRP £110.00 Now £70.00 Description Casio ensure that they have every aspect of styling and practicality covered; this watch has been produced with the young skateboarders and other thrill seekers in mind as the dial has been fitted with metal protectors to take the impact away from the mineral glass. This watch has also been fitted with the shock resistant all Casio G-Shock watches are known for. A sleek and comfortable resin strap and casing is the ideal partnership to make this watch standout. The green dial that lights up white ensures the watch has you covered in the dark. This G-Shock watch features many different features as such as an alarm, world time function that displays the time in a selected city, display flasher that signals when a selected alarm has been activated or hourly intervals, a stopwatch to ensure that all lap times can be recorded up to 24 hour worth of laps can be accumulated in one go. The dial of the G-Shock watch measures approximately 48mm in width and the watch is water resistant up to 200m and can be worn in any occasion except for scuba diving.
